items.name: Apple TV with 1080p HD
items.categoryPath: Electronics/TV & Video/Media Players & Recorders/Media Streaming Players
items.shortDescription: The Apple TV with 1080p HD gives you the best entertainment right on your widescreen TV. Choose from thousands of current and classic movies and TV shows on iTunes - many in amazing 1080p HD. Watch live sports in HD. Access content from Netflix, YouTube, Vimeo, and more. And with AirPlay, you can play video, show off photos, and enjoy music from your iPhone, iPad, or iPod touch on your New Apple TV with 1080p HD.<br><br><strong>Note:</strong> Selected titles now available on Netflix. Subscription required for Netflix. AirPlay is available on all devices running iOS 4.3 or later. Some features require the latest software. Requires second-generation Apple TV or later.

items.name: JVC Gummy Plus Inner Ear Headphones with Microphone and Remote
items.shortDescription: These JVC Gummy Pluss Inner Ear Headphones let you enjoy your favorite songs, TV shows or games discreetly. All of the parts are designed to complement the look of the Apple iPod nano 6G color so you can enjoy a more harmonious experience. These JVC headphones with microphone and remote are also compatible with iPhones and iPads, as well as Android and BlackBerry smartphones. They have a soft rubber body to deliver a comfortable fit so you can wear them for extended periods. The units deliver outstanding noise isolation so you hear more of the music that you were meant to enjoy. These JVC ear headphones have gold-plated slim plugs that provide exceptional signal quality and are resistant to corrosion. A handy inline remote control lets you adjust the volume and play songs without having to take your iPhone out of your pockets.

items.name: Beats by Dr. Dre Solo2 Wireless Headphones
items.shortDescription: Listen to music without worrying about wires thanks to the Beats by Dr. Dre Solo2 Wireless Headphones. You can unplug them and pair them with your Apple iPhone, iPad or iPod. This allows you to move freely for up to 30' of wireless listening. The solo2 headphones also let you take hands-free calls with the built-in microphone. Use the on-ear controls to adjust your listening experience without reaching for your iPhone. Stay unplugged all day thanks to the 12-hour rechargeable battery. The on ear wireless headphones have an illuminated LED fuel gauge on the headphone that lets you know when it's time to recharge. The wireless sound experience features fine-tuned acoustics for clarity, breadth and balance. All this comes in a package that is durable and has a compact folding design for easy portability. Your favorite songs sound crystal clear with rich detail, and you also can perform other functions without unplugging the beat.
items.longDescription: Make it a musical day with the Beats by Dr. Dre Solo2 Wireless Headphones.<br><b>Beats by Dr. Dre Solo2 Wireless Headphones:</b><ul><li>Pair and play wirelessly with Apple iPhone, iPad or iPod</li><li>Up to 30' Bluetooth range</li><li>Fine-tuned acoustics for clarity, breadth and balance</li><li>12-hour rechargeable battery with Fuel Gauge to indicate charge level</li><li>Built-in microphone and on-ear controls on solo2 headphones for taking calls and controlling music</li><li>Durable and compact folding design for easy portability</li></ul>

items.shortDescription: The Ematic Universal Accessory Kit for tablets and all generations of Apple iPad, with a Bluetooth speaker, charger and more, has everything you need to get the most out of your iPad or tablet. Play music wirelessly loud and clear with the wireless Bluetooth speaker. Use the Mini USB cable to charge the Ematic Accessory Kit with Portable Bluetooth Speakerbox. Use the audio splitter to connect two headphones simultaneously. The cleaning cloth is ideal for keeping your device clean. Use the car charger to charge your device while traveling. The wall charger eliminates the need for a computer when charging your iPad, iPod touch, iPhone or MP3 player. Connect directly into the speaker with the aux cable. The Ematic Universal Accessory Kit large pouch protects your iPad or tablet from bumps and scratches.
